text.tspan: *Fnetwork is a group of projects sharing and synching data
Tables shared by default: users, usermeta
Shared by active wp_posts plugin: posts, postmeta, categories...
Not shared: options, custom plugins tables
**table prefix: each project is own a shared database with custom table prefix
*2d posts tables: in our special WP configuration we (des)configure WordPress core with a custom plugin set of function to allow
sharing some post_types accross multiple installs, a clear benefy is one store/payment gateway for all projects
shared posts*, to show up in specific domain just use a categorie with it like www.grupof.com.br
